title: Natural Born Killer (Jeff Weides, Richard Bartlett)
description:
A mass shooting inside of a bar leaves two dead and a quick arrest of the gunman. But, a disturbing confession and a search of his apparent take the case in a different direction.

For episode information and photos, please visit https://anatomyofmurder.com/.
